header(class="sticky top-0 z-20 border-b border-zinc-200 bg-white/95 backdrop-blur dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-950/95")
    div(class="flex flex-col gap-3 px-5 py-4 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between")
        div
            div(class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-medium text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-globe")
                span Domains
            h1(class="mt-1 text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 도메인 관리
        div(class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
            button(type="button", (click)="syncAllZones()", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-sky-300 bg-sky-50 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-sky-800 hover:bg-sky-100 dark:border-sky-900/70 dark:bg-sky-950/30 dark:text-sky-200 dark:hover:bg-sky-950/50")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-cloud-arrow-down")
                span {{syncLoading() ? '동기화 중...' : '전체 동기화'}}
            button(type="button", (click)="openZoneModal()", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950 dark:hover:bg-zinc-200")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-plus")
                span 도메인 추가

main(class="space-y-5 px-5 py-5")
    div(*ngIf="loading()", class="h-32 rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white p-5 text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-400") 정보를 불러오는 중입니다.
    div(*ngIf="error()", class="rounded-md border border-rose-200 bg-rose-50 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-rose-700 dark:border-rose-900/70 dark:bg-rose-950/40 dark:text-rose-300") {{error()}}

    div(*ngIf="!loading() && !error()", class="space-y-5")
        section(class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-5 xl:grid-cols-[360px_1fr]")
            div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                div(class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800")
                    div
                        h2(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") Domain Zones
                        p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 도메인 이름, Zone ID, 레코드 수, 상태
                    button(type="button", (click)="openZoneModal()", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                        i(class="fa-solid fa-plus")
                        span 추가
                div(class="divide-y divide-zinc-100 dark:divide-zinc-800")
                    button(*ngFor="let zone of zones()", type="button", (click)="loadDetail(zone.id)", class="block w-full px-4 py-3 text-left transition-colors hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:hover:bg-zinc-950", [ngClass]="selectedZoneId() === zone.id ? 'bg-zinc-50 dark:bg-zinc-950' : ''")
                        div(class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3")
                            div(class="min-w-0")
                                p(class="truncate text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{zone.domain}}
                                p(class="mt-1 truncate text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{zone.zone_id}}
                            span(class="inline-flex rounded-md border px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold", [ngClass]="statusClass(zone.status)") {{zoneStatusLabel(zone)}}
                        div(class="mt-2 flex items-center gap-3 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400")
                            span Record {{zone.record_count || 0}}
                            span Last sync {{formatDate(zone.last_sync_at)}}
                    div(*ngIf="zones().length === 0", class="px-4 py-10 text-center text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 등록된 도메인이 없습니다.

            div(class="space-y-5")
                div(*ngIf="!selectedZone()", class="rounded-md border border-dashed border-zinc-300 bg-white px-6 py-16 text-center text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-400")
                    p(class="font-semibold text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200") 선택된 도메인이 없습니다.
                    p(class="mt-2") 좌측에서 도메인을 선택하거나 새 도메인을 추가하세요.

                div(*ngIf="selectedZone()", class="space-y-5")
                    div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                        div(class="flex flex-col gap-3 border-b border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800 lg:flex-row lg:items-start lg:justify-between")
                            div(class="min-w-0")
                                div(class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
                                    h2(class="truncate text-base font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{selectedZone()?.domain}}
                                    span(class="inline-flex rounded-md border px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold", [ngClass]="statusClass(selectedZone()?.status)") {{zoneStatusLabel(selectedZone())}}
                                p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") Zone ID {{selectedZone()?.zone_id}} · 레코드 {{selectedZone()?.record_count || 0}}개 · 마지막 동기화 {{formatDate(selectedZone()?.last_sync_at)}}
                                p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{selectedZone()?.last_sync_message || '아직 동기화 이력이 없습니다.'}}
                                div(class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2")
                                    span(*ngIf="sslSummaryItems().length === 0", class="inline-flex rounded-md border border-zinc-200 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300") 연결된 SSL 인증서 없음
                                    span(*ngFor="let item of sslSummaryItems()", class="inline-flex rounded-md border px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold", [ngClass]="statusClass(item.status)") {{item.label}} {{item.value}}
                            div(class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
                                button(type="button", (click)="syncSelectedZone()", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-sky-300 bg-sky-50 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-sky-800 hover:bg-sky-100 dark:border-sky-900/70 dark:bg-sky-950/30 dark:text-sky-200 dark:hover:bg-sky-950/50")
                                    i(class="fa-solid fa-arrows-rotate")
                                    span {{syncLoading() ? '동기화 중...' : '지금 동기화'}}
                                button(type="button", (click)="openZoneModal(selectedZone())", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                    i(class="fa-solid fa-pen")
                                    span 설정 수정
                                button(type="button", (click)="deleteZone(selectedZone())", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-rose-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-rose-700 hover:bg-rose-50 dark:border-rose-900/70 dark:text-rose-300 dark:hover:bg-rose-950/30")
                                    i(class="fa-solid fa-trash")
                                    span 삭제

                        div(*ngIf="detailLoading()", class="px-4 py-6 text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 상세 정보를 불러오는 중입니다.
                        div(*ngIf="!detailLoading()", class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 p-4 xl:grid-cols-[1fr_320px]")
                            div(class="space-y-4")
                                div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800")
                                    div(class="flex flex-col gap-3 border-b border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800")
                                        div(class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3")
                                            div
                                                h3(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") DNS Records
                                                p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") Type, Name, Content, Proxy, TTL을 직접 수정합니다.
                                            button(type="button", (click)="openRecordModal()", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                                i(class="fa-solid fa-plus")
                                                span 레코드 추가
                                        div(class="flex flex-col gap-3 xl:flex-row xl:items-center xl:justify-between")
                                            div(class="flex flex-wrap gap-2")
                                                button(*ngFor="let type of recordTypeOptions()", type="button", (click)="toggleRecordType(type)", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center rounded-md border px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold", [ngClass]="isRecordTypeActive(type) ? 'border-zinc-900 bg-zinc-900 text-white dark:border-zinc-100 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950' : 'border-zinc-300 text-zinc-600 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800'")
                                                    | {{type}}
                                            div(class="flex flex-1 flex-col gap-2 md:flex-row")
                                                div(*ngIf="hasIpv4Filter()", class="min-w-0 md:w-64")
                                                    wiz-component-search-select([items]="ipv4FilterItems()", [value]="recordFilters.ipv4", (valueChange)="setIpv4Filter($event)", [placeholder]="'모든 A 레코드 IP'", [searchPlaceholder]="'IP 주소 검색'", [emptyText]="'표시할 IP가 없습니다.'")
                                                input(type="text", [(ngModel)]="recordFilters.name", placeholder="Name 필터", class="h-9 min-w-0 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-xs text-zinc-900 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
                                                input(type="text", [(ngModel)]="recordFilters.content", placeholder="Content 필터", class="h-9 min-w-0 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-xs text-zinc-900 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
                                                button(type="button", (click)="resetRecordFilters()", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800") 초기화
                                    div(class="overflow-x-auto")
                                        table(class="min-w-full divide-y divide-zinc-100 text-sm dark:divide-zinc-800")
                                            thead(class="bg-zinc-50 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-400")
                                                tr
                                                    th(class="px-4 py-2 text-left font-semibold") Type
                                                    th(class="px-4 py-2 text-left font-semibold") Name
                                                    th(class="px-4 py-2 text-left font-semibold") Content
                                                    th(class="px-4 py-2 text-left font-semibold") Exposure
                                                    th(class="px-4 py-2 text-left font-semibold") TTL
                                                    th(class="px-4 py-2 text-right font-semibold") 작업
                                            tbody(class="divide-y divide-zinc-100 dark:divide-zinc-800")
                                                tr(*ngFor="let record of visibleRecords()")
                                                    td(class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{record.record_type}}
                                                    td(class="px-4 py-3 text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300")
                                                        div(class="font-medium text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100") {{record.record_name}}
                                                        div(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{fqdn(record.record_name, selectedZone()?.domain)}}
                                                    td(class="px-4 py-3 text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300")
                                                        div(class="max-w-[24rem] truncate", [attr.title]="contentPreview(record)") {{contentPreview(record)}}
                                                    td(class="px-4 py-3")
                                                        span(class="inline-flex rounded-md border px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold", [ngClass]="statusClass(record.proxied === true ? 'active' : (record.proxied === false ? 'manual' : 'pending'))") {{recordExposure(record)}}
                                                    td(class="px-4 py-3 text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300") {{record.ttl || 'auto'}}
                                                    td(class="px-4 py-3")
                                                        div(class="flex items-center justify-end gap-2")
                                                            button(type="button", (click)="openRecordModal(record)", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                                                i(class="fa-solid fa-pen")
                                                            button(type="button", (click)="deleteRecord(record)", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-rose-300 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-rose-700 hover:bg-rose-50 dark:border-rose-900/70 dark:text-rose-300 dark:hover:bg-rose-950/30")
                                                                i(class="fa-solid fa-trash")
                                                tr(*ngIf="visibleRecords().length === 0")
                                                    td(colspan="6", class="px-4 py-10 text-center text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 표시할 DNS 레코드가 없습니다.

                            div(class="space-y-4")
                                div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                                    div(class="border-b border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800")
                                        h3(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") Domain 설정
                                    div(class="space-y-3 p-4 text-sm")
                                        div
                                            p(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") Token 상태
                                            p(class="mt-1 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200") {{selectedZone()?.secret_configured ? '설정됨' : '없음'}}
                                        div
                                            p(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 마지막 메시지
                                            p(class="mt-1 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200") {{selectedZone()?.last_sync_message || '없음'}}
                                div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                                    div(class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3 border-b border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800")
                                        div
                                            h3(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") SSL 인증서
                                            p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 인증서 파일을 업로드하면 만료일과 도메인 이름을 자동으로 확인합니다.
                                        button(type="button", (click)="openCertificateModal()", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                            i(class="fa-solid fa-upload")
                                            span 업로드
                                    div(*ngIf="detail()?.ssl_certificates?.length === 0", class="px-4 py-8 text-center text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400")
                                        p 연결된 SSL 인증서가 없습니다.
                                        p(class="mt-1 text-xs") 무료 인증서 발급은 서비스 관리에서 진행합니다.
                                    div(class="divide-y divide-zinc-100 dark:divide-zinc-800")
                                        div(*ngFor="let cert of detail()?.ssl_certificates", class="px-4 py-3")
                                            div(class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3")
                                                p(class="truncate text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{cert.label || cert.cert_path}}
                                                div(class="flex items-center gap-2")
                                                    span(class="inline-flex rounded-md border px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold", [ngClass]="statusClass(cert.status)") {{certificateStatusLabel(cert.status)}}
                                                    button(type="button", (click)="deleteCertificate(cert)", class="inline-flex h-7 w-7 items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-rose-300 text-xs font-semibold text-rose-700 hover:bg-rose-50 dark:border-rose-900/70 dark:text-rose-300 dark:hover:bg-rose-950/30")
                                                        i(class="fa-solid fa-trash")
                                            p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{cert.days_remaining ?? '-'}}일 남음 · {{formatDate(cert.not_after)}} · {{cert.key_exists ? 'KEY 있음' : 'KEY 없음'}}
                                            p(class="mt-1 text-xs", [ngClass]="cert.key_matches === false || cert.key_permission_secure === false ? 'text-rose-600 dark:text-rose-300' : 'text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-300'") {{certificateKeyText(cert)}}
                                            p(class="mt-1 break-all text-[11px] text-zinc-400 dark:text-zinc-500") {{cert.cert_path}}
                                            div(*ngIf="cert.dns_names?.length > 0", class="mt-2 flex flex-wrap gap-2")
                                                span(*ngFor="let name of cert.dns_names", class="inline-flex rounded-md border border-zinc-200 px-2 py-1 text-[11px] font-medium text-zinc-600 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300") {{name}}
                                div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                                    div(class="border-b border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800")
                                        h3(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 인증서 적용 서비스
                                        p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 이 도메인 또는 하위 도메인을 사용하는 서비스입니다.
                                    div(*ngIf="serviceLinks().length === 0", class="px-4 py-8 text-center text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 연결된 서비스가 없습니다.
                                    div(class="divide-y divide-zinc-100 dark:divide-zinc-800")
                                        div(*ngFor="let item of serviceLinks()", class="px-4 py-3")
                                            div(class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3")
                                                div(class="min-w-0")
                                                    p(class="truncate text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{item.service_name}}
                                                    p(class="mt-1 break-all text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{item.domain}} · {{serviceCertificateLabel(item)}}
                                                span(class="inline-flex shrink-0 rounded-md border px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold", [ngClass]="statusClass(item.certificate_applied ? 'valid' : 'pending')") {{item.certificate_applied ? '적용됨' : '대기'}}
                                div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                                    div(class="border-b border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800")
                                        h3(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 레코드 타입 안내
                                    div(class="divide-y divide-zinc-100 dark:divide-zinc-800")
                                        div(*ngFor="let type of recordTypes()", class="px-4 py-3")
                                            p(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{type}}
                                            p(class="mt-1 text-xs leading-5 text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{recordTypeDescription(type)}}

div(*ngIf="zoneModalOpen()", class="fixed inset-0 z-50 flex items-center justify-center bg-black/50 px-4 py-6")
    div(class="w-full max-w-2xl rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white shadow-2xl dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
        div(class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-zinc-200 px-5 py-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
            div
                h2(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{zoneForm.id ? '도메인 설정 수정' : '도메인 추가'}}
                p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") Zone ID와 token은 이 도메인 전용으로 저장됩니다.
            button(type="button", (click)="closeZoneModal()", class="inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-zinc-300 text-zinc-600 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-xmark")
        div(class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 p-5 md:grid-cols-2")
            label(class="block")
                span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 도메인 이름
                input(type="text", [(ngModel)]="zoneForm.domain", placeholder="example.com", class="h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 focus:border-zinc-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
            label(class="block")
                span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") Zone ID
                input(type="text", [(ngModel)]="zoneForm.zone_id", class="h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 focus:border-zinc-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
            label(class="block md:col-span-2")
                span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") API Token
                div(class="flex items-center gap-2")
                    input([type]="zoneForm.token_visible ? 'text' : 'password'", [(ngModel)]="zoneForm.api_token_value", class="h-10 min-w-0 flex-1 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 focus:border-zinc-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
                    button(type="button", (click)="zoneForm.token_visible = !zoneForm.token_visible", class="inline-flex h-10 flex-none items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                        i(class="fa-solid", [ngClass]="zoneForm.token_visible ? 'fa-eye-slash' : 'fa-eye'")
            label(class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200")
                input(type="checkbox", [(ngModel)]="zoneForm.enabled")
                span Cloudflare 동기화 사용
        div(class="flex items-center justify-end gap-2 border-t border-zinc-200 px-5 py-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
            button(type="button", (click)="closeZoneModal()", class="inline-flex h-10 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                span 취소
            button(type="button", (click)="saveZone()", class="inline-flex h-10 items-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-4 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950 dark:hover:bg-zinc-200")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-floppy-disk")
                span 저장

div(*ngIf="recordModalOpen()", class="fixed inset-0 z-50 flex items-center justify-center bg-black/50 px-4 py-6")
    div(class="w-full max-w-3xl rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white shadow-2xl dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
        div(class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-zinc-200 px-5 py-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
            div
                h2(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{recordForm.id ? 'DNS 레코드 수정' : 'DNS 레코드 추가'}}
                p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 변경 내용은 Cloudflare API에 바로 적용되고 캐시도 함께 갱신됩니다.
            button(type="button", (click)="closeRecordModal()", class="inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-zinc-300 text-zinc-600 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-xmark")
        div(class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 p-5 md:grid-cols-2")
            label(class="block")
                span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 레코드 타입
                select([(ngModel)]="recordForm.record_type", class="h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 focus:border-zinc-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
                    option(*ngFor="let type of recordTypes()", [value]="type") {{type}}
                p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{recordTypeDescription(recordForm.record_type)}}
            label(class="block")
                span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") Name
                input(type="text", [(ngModel)]="recordForm.record_name", placeholder="@", class="h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 focus:border-zinc-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
            label(class="block md:col-span-2")
                span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") Content
                input(type="text", [(ngModel)]="recordForm.content", class="h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 focus:border-zinc-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
                p(*ngIf="aRecordHelper()", class="mt-1 text-xs text-sky-700 dark:text-sky-300") {{aRecordHelper()}}
            label(class="block")
                span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") TTL
                input(type="number", [(ngModel)]="recordForm.ttl", class="h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 focus:border-zinc-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
            label(class="block")
                span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") Priority
                input(type="number", [(ngModel)]="recordForm.priority", class="h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 focus:border-zinc-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
            label(class="block md:col-span-2")
                span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") Comment
                input(type="text", [(ngModel)]="recordForm.comment", class="h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 focus:border-zinc-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
            label(class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 md:col-span-2")
                input(type="checkbox", [(ngModel)]="recordForm.proxied")
                span Cloudflare Proxy 사용
        div(class="flex items-center justify-end gap-2 border-t border-zinc-200 px-5 py-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
            button(type="button", (click)="closeRecordModal()", class="inline-flex h-10 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                span 취소
            button(type="button", (click)="saveRecord()", class="inline-flex h-10 items-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-4 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950 dark:hover:bg-zinc-200")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-floppy-disk")
                span 저장

div(*ngIf="certificateModalOpen()", class="fixed inset-0 z-50 flex items-center justify-center bg-black/50 px-4 py-6")
    div(class="w-full max-w-2xl rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white shadow-2xl dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
        div(class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-zinc-200 px-5 py-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
            div
                h2(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") SSL 인증서 업로드
                p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{selectedZone()?.domain}}에 사용할 인증서와 개인 키 파일을 선택하세요.
            button(type="button", (click)="closeCertificateModal()", [disabled]="certificateBusy()", class="inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-zinc-300 text-zinc-600 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-xmark")
        div(class="space-y-4 p-5")
            label(class="block")
                span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 표시 이름
                input(type="text", [(ngModel)]="certificateForm.label", class="h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 focus:border-zinc-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
            div(class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-3 md:grid-cols-2")
                div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 p-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
                    p(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 인증서 파일
                    p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") PEM, CRT, CER 또는 fullchain 파일을 선택합니다.
                    input(id="domain-certificate-cert_file", type="file", accept=".pem,.crt,.cer,.cert", class="hidden", (change)="selectCertificateFile('cert_file', $event)")
                    button(type="button", (click)="openCertificateFilePicker('cert_file')", [disabled]="certificateBusy()", class="mt-3 inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                        i(class="fa-solid fa-file-arrow-up")
                        span 파일 선택
                    p(class="mt-2 truncate text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{certificateForm.cert_file_name || '선택된 파일 없음'}}
                div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 p-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
                    p(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 키 파일
                    p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 인증서와 짝이 맞는 private key 파일입니다.
                    input(id="domain-certificate-key_file", type="file", accept=".key,.pem", class="hidden", (change)="selectCertificateFile('key_file', $event)")
                    button(type="button", (click)="openCertificateFilePicker('key_file')", [disabled]="certificateBusy()", class="mt-3 inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                        i(class="fa-solid fa-file-shield")
                        span 파일 선택
                    p(class="mt-2 truncate text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{certificateForm.key_file_name || '선택된 파일 없음'}}
            div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 p-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
                p(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 체인 / Fullchain 파일
                p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 별도 chain 또는 CA bundle이 있으면 선택합니다. 선택 시 fullchain.pem으로 합쳐 저장합니다.
                input(id="domain-certificate-chain_file", type="file", accept=".pem,.crt,.cer,.chain,.bundle,.ca-bundle", class="hidden", (change)="selectCertificateFile('chain_file', $event)")
                button(type="button", (click)="openCertificateFilePicker('chain_file')", [disabled]="certificateBusy()", class="mt-3 inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                    i(class="fa-solid fa-link")
                    span 파일 선택
                p(class="mt-2 truncate text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{certificateForm.chain_file_name || '선택하지 않음'}}
        div(class="flex items-center justify-end gap-2 border-t border-zinc-200 px-5 py-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
            button(type="button", (click)="closeCertificateModal()", [disabled]="certificateBusy()", class="inline-flex h-10 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                span 취소
            button(type="button", (click)="uploadCertificate()", [disabled]="certificateBusy()", class="inline-flex h-10 items-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-4 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 disabled:opacity-60 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950 dark:hover:bg-zinc-200")
                i(class="fa-solid", [ngClass]="certificateBusy() ? 'fa-spinner fa-spin' : 'fa-upload'")
                span {{certificateBusy() ? '업로드 중' : '업로드'}}
